   3.692552404830366*^9}, {3.6925525421130323`*^9, 
   3.6925525440880213`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"1dadfb3f-42e0-4f29-95f9-\
f77945245cc9"],

Cell["\<\
This routine filters a set of options such that only the options which are \
possibly appropriate to a PulseSequence element are passed down to it. \
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.69227426874146*^9, 3.692274334002482*^9}, {
  3.692274498402402*^9, 3.6922745001741037`*^9}, {3.6925508531719847`*^9, 
  3.692550879881074*^9}, {3.6925524104496517`*^9, 
  3.692552444622159*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"968a211d-b4b4-4b78-adf6-\
ae20e0209efb"],

Cell["\<\
Any option is passed down unless it clearly belongs to a different \
PulseSequence element\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.692552493556529*^9, 
  3.6925525167404633`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"7a67820b-8016-40ca-b9dc-\
abba55ae92d4"],

