Cell["\<\
LocalGeneratorSymbols is called in order to identify symbols that are local \
to routines such as TimeDependentGeneratorFunction etc., and which should not \
be detected as non-numeric symbols, in advance of numerical computations. The \
ShapedPulse symbol, which contains local arguments, is added to this list. \
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.74436619699299*^9, 3.744366331753867*^9}, 
   3.816848201747924*^9},ExpressionUUID->"b60f1e73-b7be-4024-b28c-\
d87830d1be6e"],

