Cell["\<\
a problem has been encountered where a PulseSequence contains another \
PulseSequence which contains a flexible delay. Resolution of the timing \
should be enabled if the outer PulseSequence has a defined duration. The \
error trap below has been disabled to allow this to be sorted out, since this \
error triggers prematurely in this case. \
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.692277485877186*^9, 
